        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "Notes\n- This is the widely accepted standard potential for the Cu²⁺/Cu(s) couple under standard-state conditions.  \n- SRD‑46 focuses on stability constants rather than electrode potentials; however, its bibliography indexes canonical sources for E° values. Relevant entries include Latimer, Oxidation Potentials, 2nd ed. (1952) [lit_1741; via vlm_172912], and general electrode-potential/ISE references (e.g., lit_13915 “85VP”).",
